<div type="abstract"><head>Rat an Heinrich d. J. Hutt</head><p>Der Rat lädt den Adressaten für kommenden Dienstag vor.</p>
</div>
<!--This div could possibly contain the analytic portion of the edition.-->
<div type="linguisticAnalysis"><ab><w join="" lemma="" msd="" part="" pos=""><fLib><f name=" "/></fLib></w></ab></div>
</front>
<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_505" id="251v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab facs="#facs_505_r1l23"><expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Hutten dem <expan>Jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan> </ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_505_r1l24"><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan> <expan>heınr<ex>ich</ex></expan> wır befelhen vnd <expan>gepıete<ex>n</ex></expan> dır bey dem eyde . den du vns </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l25">vmb dein nehſte <expan>loſu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> getan haſt / daʒ du auf den nehſten ertag </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l26">ʒu ratʒeıt für vns komeſt vnd da <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemeſt</expan> was wır mıt dır </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l27">reden <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> vnd des niht laſſeſt <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>ſ<ex>ub</ex></expan> ſıgıllo <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>iſt</ex>rıcıuıu<ex>m</ex></expan> </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_505_r1l28"><expan>f<ex>er</ex>ıa</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi> <expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> matheȷ </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_505" id="251v"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee">
<ab><expan>H<ex>einrich</ex></expan> Hutten dem
                        <expan>jüng<ex>er</ex>n</expan></ab>
</div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieber</ex></expan>
<expan>Heinr<ex>ich</ex></expan>, wir befelhen und
                            <expan>gepiete<ex>n</ex></expan> dir bey dem eyde, den du uns umb dein
                        nehste <expan>losu<ex>n</ex>g</expan> getan hast, daz du auf den nehsten
                        ertag zu ratzeit für uns komest und da <expan>v<ex>er</ex>nemest</expan>,
                        was wir mit dir reden <expan>w<ex>er</ex>den</expan> und des niht lassest.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>s<ex>ub</ex></expan> sigillo
                            <expan>m<ex>a</ex>g<ex>ist</ex>ri</expan>
<expan>civiu<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>f<ex>er</ex>ia</expan> v<hi rend="sup">a</hi>
<expan>an<ex>te</ex></expan> Mathei.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
